results.name: Triangle read by rows: DX(n,d) = number of properly d-dimensional polyominoes with n cells, modulo translations (n>=1, 0 <= d <= n-1).
comment: According to Barequet-Barequet-Rote, p. 260, the value DX(7, 6) = 134209 given by W. F. Lunnon is incorrect; it should be 153664, see A127670; this also affects A195762 which is the right-hand diagonal of this sequence. - _Alexander Knapp_, May 13 2013
link: R. Barequet, G. Barequet, and G. Rote, Formulae and growth rates of high-dimensional polycubes, Combinatorica 30 (2010), pp. 257-275.
W. F. Lunnon, Counting multidimensional polyominoes. Computer Journal 18 (1975), no. 4, pp. 366-367.
xref: Diagonals (with formulas) are A127670, A171860, A191092, A259015, A290738.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Sep 23 2011
